	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Foreman's Tunic is not a bad item for the price, but I think you'll get more bang for your plat if you get the Wu's.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you buy the Foreman's, it will probably cost you all of your 150pp, whereas, with the Wu's, you should have money left over to upgrade a couple more of your raw/cured silk pieces to their Wu's counterparts.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
