	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have heard after a certain lvl monks get a inate damage bonus.&nbsp;&nbsp;What is this all about?  First of all is it true or BS?  Secondly does it pertain to H2H or all combat abilites?  Thirdly is there a formula or something you can follow to know what your damage bonus is at that lvl?  Ty for your time<br><br><br>Zwack 36 iksar monk<br>M Marr<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
