	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bleh I wish you hadn't burned your skill points.&nbsp;&nbsp;You'll get much better return on them with Feign Death and Instill Doubt.<br><br>Don't sweat the skill numbers - you WILL slow down in leveling, and they'll have more time to catch up.  It's not a bad idea to get a light fast 2HB like a bamboo bo stick, and use it to work on your 2HB skill every so often.  Your skills will catch up just fine by your 20s - just try to get some 2HB in here and there.<br><br>I made the mistake of letting 2HB lag horribly, and found myself asking full groups if I could be a non-xp 7th on their mobs when I was in my 30s to catch my 2HB up.  But it didn't take all that long.<br><br>In short, you've got the right idea - keep up with all your skills.  But at 12 you don't need to worry it too much yet.<br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
