	   <tr><td colspan=2>By FS I'm guessing you mean IFS or RFS<br><br>IFS = Imbued Fighter's Staff.&nbsp;&nbsp;38/40 drops in Sebilis.<br><br>RFS = Runed Fighter's Staff.  19/20 no longer drops.<br><br>With the recent mods to 2HB, IFS &gt; RFS<br><br>TStaff = Tranquil Staff 29/30 Proc 120 direct damage (unresistable) plus a stun that ranges from 0 to 10 seconds.<br><br>TStaff is arguably the best tradeable monk 2HB in the game.<br><br>All of the above go for big money.  IFS &gt;10k, TStaff &gt;30-60k depending on server.<br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
