	   <tr><td colspan=2>Until you're in your 30s, you want the best weapon in your primary hand regardless of speed.&nbsp;&nbsp;Speed is irrelevant with regard to damage output till then.  Just go with the best weapon ratio in your primary.<br><br>Weapon Ratio = (Damage*2+1)/(Delay/10)<br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
