	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Go with CoT in primary and PSU in secondary. This is actually an easy decision at any level since the CoT has both a better ratio and is a faster weapon. Until you get a really high damage bonus you will get better results with the better ratio in the primary hand. To calculate for individual weapons you have go to www.monkly-business.com and check up the guide on modal damage. By working through the calculations you will see which weapon works best in which hand.<br><br>Right now at level 32 I am using a KD in primary and wu's stick in secondary. Around level 45 or so it will probably work better to switch hands because of the damage bonus.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
