	   <tr><td colspan=2>Lets see, getting money at lvl 8 was tough lol.&nbsp;&nbsp;Obviously selling silk to taliors and bone chips to necros can get you a few pp to start.  Selling DB belts to those looking to for faction works also in EC (or CB belts in GFD).  You can sell wolf/bear pelts and get some pp from taliors.  I really didn't start making money until I was about 12th and started hunting Will-o-Wisps in WC.  The other option is to try and get to a place well above your level.  Here you can loot from MOBs that no one else wanted.  I do not recommend this for two reasons:  1. It is easy to die (and if over 10th a long cr lol), 2. You could get a bad rap like you were describing.  My advice is to enjoy the levels as you go through them (this is a game that you are paying for lol), and pick up the spare pp as it comes.  Your equipment is great to start with (but no one will accuse you of being a heavy twink) and money will eventually come :)<br><br><br>Good Luck<br><br>Uniero<br>46th Human Monk<br>Officer Odin's Ghost<br>7th Hammer    <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
