	   <tr><td colspan=2>Lonaleb,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;The gear you mention should carry you well into your teens and still be excellent.  I had basically the same set up well into 17.  The first upgrades you would be looking for:<br>1.  Ears: BS Electum earrings 500pp each<br>2.  Neck: Ulthork Hide Collar 75pp<br>3.  Face: Snarak Mask 500pp (Many options out there)<br>4.  Arms:  In order Wu's, Gator Scale, Azure<br>5.  Chest:  CCS 200pp (or Spore Covered Tunic for 75pp, or Lock Jaw for 25pp)<br>6.  Shoulders:  Drovlag Mantle 75pp<br>7.  Wrist:  Good for a long time, next Acrylia Reinforced Bracers (400 pp) each.<br>8.  Fingers:  6/65 500pp each<br>9.  Feet:  Wu's 65pp<br>10. Legs:  Wu's followed by Gator Scale<br>11. Hands:  Gem Inlaid Gaunts 150pp<br>12.  Weapons:  Fighting Baton (300pp) or CoT (600pp) for 1 HB, a Polished Steel Ulak for H2H (250pp).<br><br>Warning:  This list stresses AC first and foremost followed by HP then Stamina.  If you feel Strength, Dex, or Agility are more important than your list will vary.<br><br>Good Luck,<br><br>Uniero<br>46th Human Monk<br>Officer Odin's Ghost<br>7th Hammer<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
